room_title: Escape room "Escape the Supervillain’s Lair" by Whole Brain Escape in Raleigh - Durham
room_description: It’s 1963, and supervillains have taken over the world. You and your fellow superheroes have been captured by the nefarious Quizzler. She’s neutralized your super-powers, so you’ll have to use your wits to escape. Are you ready?
